## Overview

YouTubeBot is a **fully automated pipeline** that creates and uploads 2 motivational YouTube videos per day. It uses:

| Component | Technology | Cost |
|-----------|-----------|------|
| Script Writing | **Groq API** (Llama 3.3 70B) | Free |
| Voiceover | **Microsoft Edge TTS** | Free |
| Video Background | **Local stock footage** (MP4 clips) | Free |
| Background Music | **Local MP3** file | Free |
| Thumbnail | **Pillow** (Python) | Free |
| Upload | **YouTube Data API v3** | Free |
| Video Processing | **FFmpeg** | Free |

### Pipeline Flow

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[02_write_script.py] --> B[03_voiceover.py]
    B --> C[04_get_footage.py]
    C --> D[05_make_video.py]
    D --> E[06_thumbnail.py]
    E --> F[07_upload.py]
```

---

## Architecture

### Entry Points

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [main.py](file:///d:/YouTubeBot/main.py) | **Production** — Runs full pipeline × 2, uploads to YouTube, schedules at optimal IST times |
| [test_main.py](file:///d:/YouTubeBot/test_main.py) | **Testing** — Runs pipeline × 2 but skips upload, saves to [temp/](file:///d:/YouTubeBot/test_main.py#39-72) folder for review |

### Production Schedule ([main.py](file:///d:/YouTubeBot/main.py))

The bot creates 2 videos per day, scheduled for optimal Indian audience engagement:

| Video | Publish Time (IST) | Upload Time (UTC) | Why |
|-------|-------------------|-------------------|-----|
| Video 1 | 12:00 PM IST | 06:30 UTC | Lunch break — people scroll during break |
| Video 2 | 6:00 PM IST | 12:30 UTC | After work/school — highest India traffic |

