## Troubleshooting

| Issue | Likely Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------------|-----|
| `ERROR: No clips found in stock/` | Empty stock folder | Add MP4 clips to [stock/](file:///d:/YouTubeBot/scripts/06_thumbnail.py#11-51) subfolders |
| `stock_concat.txt not found` | Step 4 didn't run | Run [04_get_footage.py](file:///d:/YouTubeBot/scripts/04_get_footage.py) first |
| FFmpeg error during assembly | Clips not normalizing | Check FFmpeg is in PATH: `ffmpeg -version` |
| No voiceover files | Edge TTS failed | Check internet connection (Edge TTS needs it) |
| Groq API error | Bad API key or rate limit | Check [.env](file:///d:/YouTubeBot/.env) GROQ_API_KEY, wait if rate-limited |
| Upload fails | OAuth expired or invalid | Delete [output/token.json](file:///d:/YouTubeBot/output/token.json) and re-authenticate |
| Thumbnail upload fails | Channel not verified | Visit [youtube.com/verify](https://youtube.com/verify) |
| Video looks corrupted | Old concat bug (pre-fix) | Ensure you have the latest [05_make_video.py](file:///d:/YouTubeBot/scripts/05_make_video.py) with normalization |
